        "## Data Preprocessing and Exploration\n",
        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Perform initial data exploration to understand the structure, identify missing values, handle categorical features, and prepare the data for the various models. This may include feature scaling, encoding, and, if necessary, combining the two datasets. For supervised models, identify or define a target variable.\n"
