      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "First, I'll combine the `ganga_df` and `sangam_df` DataFrames into a single DataFrame called `combined_df`. Then, I'll convert the 'Date' column to datetime objects. After that, I'll check for any missing values in `combined_df` and impute them if necessary, since the `info()` output in the previous step showed no missing values, so I'll skip the imputation step if there are no missing values. Next, I'll encode the 'Status' categorical column using Label Encoding, as it's intended to be a target variable. Finally, I'll scale the numerical features using `StandardScaler` to prepare them for modeling.\n",
        "\n"
      ]
